{"type":"text","timestamp":1781762474480,"sessionID":"ses_126b15e64ffeXip2YXWt9pDpCA","part":{"id":"prt_ed951b05e001Q23hDZXzPfB0KZ","messageID":"msg_ed951871d0016kbaZZmtLBSEr4","sessionID":"ses_126b15e64ffeXip2YXWt9pDpCA","type":"text","text":"A concrete risk candidate emerged in the launcher session proxy: `memory_save` is classified replayable despite an in-code note that secondary index writes can duplicate after commit-then-die. I’m checking the save path before recording it as a finding.","time":{"start":1781762469982,"end":1781762474478},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0cca643c2d3862c5016a3389a5d80c8191b968647812ad02f3","phase":"commentary"}}}}
